{"tid":1618063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[蒙面法] 好奇想知靠沙士上位嘅陳馮富珍點睇蒙面法","createTime":"2019-10-04T03:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:25:31.000Z","uid":294981,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e87a83af4f38f8329401adb2811cb1ad910af5f","tid":1618063,"uid":294981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人病左仲可唔可以戴口罩呢？？？<br />\n最近轉季喎！ 應該好快又到流感高峰期 ！<br />\n如果有人可以問下呢位前世衛總幹事同世衛就好喇！"},{"pid":"4d00f33d959472c32d57f0a63cf7f6766c65feb4","tid":1618063,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"奶共狗"},{"pid":"24c46a94d3cc30a8c84302004b3f7272a11c5803","tid":1618063,"uid":294981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e87a83af4f38f8329401adb2811cb1ad910af5f","tid":1618063,"uid":294981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人病左仲可唔可以戴口罩呢？？？<br />\n最近轉季喎！ 應該好快又到流感高峰期 ！<br />\n如果有人可以問下呢位前世衛總幹事同世衛就好喇！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"其實香港人戴口罩嘅習慣唔係今年６月先開始，而係2003年！！！<br />\n<br />\n沙士之後， 病咗要戴口罩係香港成為常識！之後仲推左陳馮富珍上世衛做幹事！<br />\n<br />\n宜家你問陳馮富珍，佢應該唔敢答喇...<br />\n<br />\n但對於世衛黎講，香港係世界衛生史=沙士；<br />\n戴口罩嘅意義係預防同阻止疾病擴散，<br />\n所以如果你問世衛(<a href=\"https://twitter.com/who\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwho&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=85d30c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/who</a>) : Should I wear a mask if I'm sick/having a cold/etc?<br />\n世衛一定答 yes, you should!<br />\n世衛會認為唔俾戴口罩係nonsense!<br />\n好彩嘅話，世衛可能仲會同港共政府割席！<br />\n<br />\n而下一個流感高峰期，班狗官同建制派絕對會成為the one to blame!"}]}